name: Personalised Noah's Ark Print
description:
This adorable Noah's ark print beautifully captures this much loved bible story.

Children will love exploring all the different animal characters and will have fun spotting something different each time they look!

This personalised illustration will be the perfect backdrop for any nursery or child's bedroom. Inspired by the birth of our closest friends first child 'Noah', this print is ideal as a gift for a new baby, christening present or child's birthday, or as a special keepsake for you and your little one to treasure.

Your personalised Noah's ark print is custom made to order using your chosen name and date of birth ,eg., Noah, 25th March 2012.

Your colour choices are:

Baby Blue, Baby Pink, Atlantis Green, Ocean Blue or Warm Grey

Personalised Message: To make your print even more extra special you can request a handwritten pencilled message (maximum of 50 characters), eg Welcome to the world Poppy Olive Gosling! x

Please let us know the name, date of birth and personal message through the “comments to seller” at the PayPal checkout or via "contact" on our home page. 

Made from:
All our prints are handmade and printed on High White Stonemarque 300gsm acid free textured paper using the finest pigment inks. Please be aware that different computers will reproduce the colours slightly differently and therefore the colours on your computer might appear slightly different from the print-out poster.

Dimensions:
Paper size: 32 cm x 45 cm. This print can fit into a standard 'off the shelf' frame.

Please note that picture frames are not included and are for display purposes only.

All our prints are sold unframed, carefully wrapped in tissue paper and then sent in a sturdy cardboard tube. Your print will be dispatched to you within a week of your order.


Thank you for shopping with us.
